        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This specialized razor disc (Hardness 11, HP 84, BT 42) was originally designed by the members of Clan Molgrade for use by Highhelm's soldiers. The integrated blades are etched with runes, making them a *+1 striking* weapon.",
